%20away%20the%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20election%20team's%20squad.%20There%20was%20a%20box%20in%20the%20car.%20You%20can%20see%20the%20kit.%20You%20will%20see%20we%20have%20the%20publicity%20material.%20It%20contains%20Modi%20face%20masks%2C%20caps%20and%20other%20publicity%20material%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20underlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Badgujar%20blamed%20the%20opposition%20of%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20defaming%20the%20national%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20gold%20biscuit%20that%20you%20are%20talking%20about.%20This%20is%20that%20plastic%20biscuit.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20biscuit%20but%20a%20perfume%20bottle%2C%20but%20the%20opposition%20has%20to%20make%20a%20mountain%20out%20of%20a%20molehill.%20So%20they%20are%20calling%20perfume%20bottle%20a%20gold%20biscuit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20further%20explained%20that%20he%20was%20made%20to%20wait%20at%20the%20police%20station%20for%20hours%20and%20out%20of%20frustration%20referred%20to%20the%20plastic%20bottle%20as%20gold%20biscuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20called%20it%20so.%20It%20was%20late%20in%20the%20night%2C%20the%20squad%20was%20not%20listening%20to%20us.%20We%20were%20called%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20made%20to%20sit%20for%203-4%20hours.%20We%20were%20angry%20and%20when%20we%20were%20asked%20what%20is%20this%2C%20I%20said%2C%20'See%20it%20for%20yourself.%20It%20is%20gold%20biscuit'.%20When%20we%20said%20it%20is%20nothing%2C%20they%20did%20not%20understand.%20Then%20what%20will%20someone%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20BJP%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20clarified%20that%20it%20was%20his%20own%20daughter%20who%20put%20out%20the%20video%20where%20he%20can%20be%20heard%20calling%20the%20bottle%20gold%20biscuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EChunaav%20ka%20mahaul%20hone%20ki%20wajah%20se%20sabko%20aisa%20lag%20raha%20hai.%20Viksit%20bharat%20banne%20jaa%20raha%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(