3BIt%20happens%20when%20the%20sun%20gets%20to%20the%20peak%20of%20its%20activity%20of%20the%2011-year%20circle.%20After%20every%2011%20years%2C%20the%20activity%20of%20the%20sun%20goes%20from%20high%20to%20low%20and%20in%202025%20the%20activity%20is%20going%20to%20be%20at%20its%20peak%2C%26quot%3B%20scientific%20officer%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20Plasma%20Research%20Centre%20Dr%20Ravi%20AV%20Kumar%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rarity%20of%20this%20solar%20storm%20harks%20back%20to%20October%202003%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration's%20(NOAA)%20space%20weather%20prediction%20centre%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20celestial%20occurrence%20not%20seen%20in%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chance%20of%20solar%20flares%20coming%20out%20at%20this%20time%20are%20more%2C%20as%20these%20are%20highly%20charged%20particles%20of%20plasma%20which%20can%20travel%20at%20very%20high%20velocities%2C%20the%20scientist%20said.%20The%20faster%20these%20particles%20move%20the%20more%20dangerous%20they%20are%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20these%20are%20charged%20particles%20from%20the%20Sun%2C%20they%20can%20get%20deflected%20from%20the%20Earth's%20magnetic%20field.%20Some%20of%20these%20deflected%20particles%20can%20come%20to%20polar%20regions%20of%20the%20Earth%2C%20which%20then%20interact%20with%20gas%20molecules%20in%20the%20upper%20atmosphere%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20They%20produce%20a%20colour%20called%20Aurora.%20When%20there%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20solar%20flare%20like%20the%20one%20which%20happened%20yesterday%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20Earth's%20atmosphere%20and%20magnetic%20field%2C%20it%20produces%20Auroras.%20People%20are%20very%20fortunate%20to%20even%20see%20this%20right%20up%20to%20northern%20Italy%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Aurora%20could%20also%20be%20seen%20in%20Ladakh...%20Flares%20come%20and%20go%3B%20they%20don't%20affect%20us%20directly%20but%20can%20affect%20our%20day-to-day%20activities%20like%20communication%20as%20the%20satellites%20can%20be%20disrupted.%20Satellite%20TV%20signals%20and%20radio%20communication%20could%20also%20get%20disrupted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20scientist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Ahmedabad%20Gujarat%3A%20On%20Solar%20Storm%2C%20Scientific%20Officer%20of%20Institute%20for%20Plasma%20Research%20Centre%20Dr%20Ravi%20A%20V%20Kumar%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BSolar%20Flares%20are%20very%20common%2C%20it%20happens%20all%20the%20time...It%20happens%20when%20the%20sun%20gets%20to%20the%20peak%20of%20its%20activity%20of%2011-year%20circle...After%20every%2011...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8w8ejhiQd4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F8w8ejhiQd4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1789271712179122583%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolar%20cycles%2C%20characterised%20by%20fluctuations%20in%20sunspot%20activity%2C%20dictate%20the%20sun's%20behaviour%2C%20transitioning%20from%20periods%20of%20relative%20calm%20to%20intense%20activity%20and%20back%20again.%20The%20current%20cycle%2C%20Solar%20Cycle%2025%2C%20has%20exceeded%20expectations%20in%20terms%20of%20activity%2C%20with%20NOAA's%20Space%20Weather%20Prediction%20Center%20noting%20an%20uptick%20in%20sunspot%20counts%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20cycle's%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20ANI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715438400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F0smknvu4_slar-storm-reuters_625x300