n%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20discussed%20your%20invitation%20with%20the%20Congress%20President%2C%20Shri%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20Ji.%20We%20agree%20that%20such%20a%20debate%20will%20help%20people%20understand%20our%20respective%20vision%20and%20enable%20them%20to%20make%20an%20informed%20choice.%20It%20is%20also%20critical%20to%20put%20to%20rest%20any%20unsubstantiated%20allegations%20attributed%20to%20our%20respective%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Congress%20president%20said%20in%20a%20response%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20principal%20parties%20fighting%20the%20election%2C%20the%20public%20deserve%20to%20hear%20from%20their%20leaders%20directly.%20Accordingly%2C%20either%20myself%20or%20the%20Congress%20President%20would%20be%20pleased%20to%20participate%20in%20such%20a%20debate.%20Please%20do%20let%20us%20know%20if%20and%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20agrees%20to%20participate%2C%20following%20which%20we%20can%20discuss%20the%20details%20and%20format%20of%20the%20debate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20event%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Wayanad%20MP%20had%20been%20asked%20about%20the%20invitation%20and%20he%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20100%25%20ready%20to%20debate%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20But%20I%20know%20the%20PM%2C%20he%20will%20not%20agree%20to%20a%20debate%20with%20me.%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20can%20also%20take%20part%20in%20such%20a%20debate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20seen%20debates%20between%20contenders%20for%20the%20President's%20post%20since%201947%2C%20when%20two%20Republican%20contenders%20agreed%20to%20a%20verbal%20duel%20which%20was%20broadcast%20on%20radio%20and%20the%20first%20televised%20debate%20took%20place%20in%201952.%20Barring%20a%20few%20years%2C%20the%20debates%20have%20been%20a%20fixture%20of%20the%20American%20political%20landscape%20since%20then%20and%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20voters%20to