%2C%20strapping%20detainees%20down%20to%20their%20beds%2C%20blindfolding%20them%2C%20and%20holding%20them%20in%20diapers%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F05%2F10%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-sde-teiman-detention-whistleblowers-intl-cmd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20CNN%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sde%20Teiman%20camp%20in%20the%20Negev%20desert%20in%20southern%20Israel%20is%20also%20a%20military%20base.%20It%20has%20been%20the%20site%20of%20abusive%20conduct%20against%20some%20of%20the%2070%20Palestinian%20detainees%2C%20three%20Israeli%20whistleblowers%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedical%20personnel%20at%20the%20facility%20are%20alleged%20to%20have%20performed%20amputations%20on%20prisoners%20due%20to%20injuries%20sustained%20from%20prolonged%20handcuffing%2C%20with%20some%20procedures%20carried%20out%20by%20underqualified%20staff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuards%20are%20accused%20of%20using%20excessive%20force%20as%20a%20form%20of%20punishment%2C%20while%20detainees%20endure%20routine%20humiliations%2C%20including%20being%20attacked%20by%20dogs%20and%20subjected%20to%20aggressive%20searches%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20detained%20the%20prisoners%20during%20the%20on-going%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%2C%20that%20began%20after%20Hamas%20militants%20surged%20into%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20committing%20massacres%20and%20atrocities%20that%20left%201%2C200%20people%20dead%2C%20and%20230%20hostages%20kidnapped%20to%20Gaza.%20Israel's%20siege%20of%20Gaza%20that%20followed%20has%20killed%2034%2C000%2C%20including%20thousands%20of%20children%2C%20says%20the%20Hamas-run%20Ministry%20of%20Health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20whistleblower%20told%20CNN%20that%20beatings%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20done%20to%20gather%20intelligence.%20They%20were%20done%20out%20of%20revenge.%20It%20was%20punishment%20for%20what%20they%20did%20on%20October%207%20and%20punishment%20for%20behavior%20in%20the%20camp.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuards%20strip%20them%20down%20of%20%26quot%3Banything%20that%20resembles%20human%20beings%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20whistleblower%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20field%20hospital%2C%20wounded%20detainees%20were%20strapped%20to%20beds%2C%20dressed%20in%20diapers%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20fed%20through%20straws%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palestinians%20who%20were%20detained%20during%20the%20Israeli%20army%20attacks%20on%20Shifa%20Hospital%20are%20brought%20to%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20Martyrs%20Hospital%20for%20treatment%20after%20their%20release%20in%20Deir%20Al%20Balah%2C%20Gaza%20on%20March%2024%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663f5722b4abc992e8c8a95d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalestinians%20who%20were%20detained%20during%20the%20Israeli%20army%20attacks%20on%20Shifa%20Hospital%20are%20brought%20to%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20Martyrs%20Hospital%20for%20treatment%20after%20their%20release%20in%20Deir%20Al%20Balah%2C%20Gaza%20on%20March%2024%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%20%7C%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mohammed%20Al-Ran%2C%20headed%20the%20surgical%20unit%20at%20Gaza's%20Indonesian%20hospital%2C%20a%20former%20prisoner%20in%20the%20Sde%20Teiman%20camp%2C%20told%20CNN%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20removed%20my%20blindfold%2C%20I%20could%20see%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20humiliation%20and%20abasement%2C%20I%20could%20see%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20they%20saw%20us%20not%20as%20human%20beings%20but%20as%20animals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%20operates%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Combatants%20Law%2C%20granting%20the%20military%20broad%20powers%20to%20detain%20individuals%20without%20due%20process%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20transparency%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20permits%20the%20military%20to