to%20them.%20Also%2C%20thank%20you%20to%20the%20players%20and%20coaches%20who%20have%20made%20this%20the%20best%20job%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20excited%20for%20the%20new%20challenges%20that%20lie%20ahead%2C%20as%20well%20as%20filling%20my%20days%20with%20even%20more%20golf.%20Thank%20you%20to%20everyone%20who%20has%20supported%20me%20over%20the%20years%2C%20it's%20always%20meant%20a%20lot%2C%20even%20if%20my%20face%20often%20doesn't%20show%20it.%20See%20you%20at%20the%20Test%2C%20Go%20well%20Jimmy%20x%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC604ETbNpu-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC604ETbNpu-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC604ETbNpu-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC604ETbNpu-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20James%20Anderson%20(%40jimmya9)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20'The%20Guardian'%2C%20Anderson%20was%20told%20by%20England's%20Test%20team%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Brendon%20McCullum%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F290-brendon-mccullum-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBrendon%20McCullum%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20future%2C%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20Ashes%202025-26%20in%20Australia%2C%20which%20means%20that%20end%20of%20the%20road%20is%20near%20for%20the%2041-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20McCullum%20flew%20especially%20from%20New%20Zealand%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20inform%20Anderson%20about%20his%20future%20over%20a%20round%20of%20golf%20Anderson%2C%20who%20has%20played%20187%20Tests%20for%20England%20in%20a%20storied%20career%20which%20began%20in%20May%202003%20along%20with%20194%20ODIs%20and%2019%20T20Is%2C%20sits%20third%20in%20the%20list%20of%20all-time%20highest%20wicket-takers%20in%20Test%20cricket%20with%20700%20wickets%2C%20behind%20Warne%20(708)%20and%20Sri%20Lanka's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Muttiah%20Muralitharan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F313-muttiah-muralidaran-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMuttiah%20Muralitharan%3C%2Fa%3E%20(800).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715431200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F70vft8do_james-anderson-rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_24_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafter-21-years-and-700-test-wickets-james-anderson-says-he-will-retire-his-last-test-will-be-5640235%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22James%20Anderson%20has%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20retire%20from%20cricket%20this%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Betrayed%20By%20Indore%20Pick%2C%20Congress%20Bats%20For%20NOTA%20To%20%26quot%3BTeach%20BJP%20A%20Lesson%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJolted%20by%20its%20Indore%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20withdrawing%20its%20nomination%20and%20then%20rubbing%20salt%20in%20its%20wounds%20by%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20now%20banking%20on%20the%20NOTA%20-%20none%20of%20the%20above%20-%20option%20to%20%26quot%3Bteach%20a%20lesson%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20not%20won%20the%20Indore%20constituency%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20biggest%20in%20terms%20of%20voters%2C%20in%2035%20years%20(since%201989)%2C%20but%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20it%20has%20not%20even%20been%20able%20to%20field%20a%20candidate.%20The%20BJP's%20nominee%20is%20sitting%20MP%20Shankar%20Lalwani%20and%20the%20Congress%20had%20given%20a%20ticket%20to%20Akshay%20Kanti%20Bam%2C%20who%20quit%20the%20race%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20withdrawing%20nominations%20and%20then%20proceeded%20to%20quit%20the%20party%20as%20well%2C%20switching%20over%20to%20its%20rival.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20its%20substitute%20candidate's%20petition%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20constituency%20on%20the%20party's%20symbol%20was%20denied%20by%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20launched%20a%20high-octane%20push%20for%20NOTA%20votes%20and%20has%20also%20forced%20a%20response%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20whose%20campaign%20was%20seen%20as%20having%20slackened%20since%20it%20did%20not%20see%20much%20competition%20from%20the%2013%20other%20candidates%20still%20in%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndore%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20fourth%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Jitu%20Patwari%20has%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20not%20support%20any%20of%20the%20remaining%20candidates%20and%20urged%20people%20to%20create%20a%20record%20of%20NOTA%20votes%20to%20punish%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Sajjan%20Verma%2C%20a%20former%20minister%20and%20former%20MP%2C%20said%20in%20Hindi%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Indore...%20Our%20Congress%20candidate%20has%20been%20stolen%20by%20some%20people%2C%20who%20have%20deprived%20you%20of%20your%20right%20to%20vote.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20teach%20them%20a%20lesson%2C%20press%20the%20NOTA%20button%20and%20save%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoters%20of%20Indore%20had%20delivered%20a%20huge%20victory%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20last%20municipal%20and%20assembly%20elections.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20BJP%20murdered%20democracy%20by%20unfairly%20luring%20Mr%20Bam.%20Voters%20must%20give%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20BJP%20by%20picking%20the%20NOTA%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Shobha%20Ojha%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NOTA%20option%20was%20introduced%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20directions%20in%202013%20and%20has%20given%20voters%20a%20way%20to%20express%20their%20dissatisfaction%20with%20all%20the%20candidates%20contesting%20the%20elections.%20The%20votes%20given%20to%20%C2%A0NOTA%20do%20not%20impact%20the%20polls%20in%20any%20way%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20last%20month%20on%20a%20petition%20seeking%20that%20an%20election%20in%20a%20constituency%20be%20declared%20void%20if%20the%20majority%20of%20voters%20choose%20NOTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Attack%20On%20Democracy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWary%20of%20the%20optics%20of%20a%20record%20number%20of%20votes%20going%20to%20NOTA%2C%20however%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20called%20the%20Congress'%20campaign%20a%20%26quot%3Bnegative%20tactic%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Battack%20on%20democracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20BJP%20Councillor%20Sandhya%20Yadav%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20removing%20a%20poster%20pasted%20on%20an%20auto%20by%20an%20organisation%20called%20the%20'Loktantra%20Bachao%20Samiti'%20(Save%20Democracy%20Committee)%20asking%20people%20to%20cast%20their%20votes%20for%20NOTA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20Ms%20Yadav%20told%20PTI%20that%20she%20would%20continue%20to%20remove%20such%20posters%20and%20that%20promoting%20the%20voting%20option%20was%20not%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20BJP%20chief%20VD%20Sharma%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Binstigating%26quot%3B%20people%20to%20press%20NOTA%20was%20a%20crime%20in%20democracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Should%20Not%20Have%20Happened'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20speaker%20Sumitra%20Mahajan%20-%20who%20has%20won%20from%20Indore%20eight%20times%20-%20however%2C%20called%20the%20last-minute%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20unfair%20and%20said%20voters%20have%20a%20right%20to%20decide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20surprised%20to%20know%20about%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20nomination%20of%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%20candidate%20in%20Indore...%20This%20should%20not%20have%20happened.%20There%20was%20no%20need%20for%20this%20development%20as%20it%20was%20written%20on%20the%20wall%20that%20nobody%20can%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%20Indore%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20some%20people%20from%20the%20city%20had%20called%20her%20up%20to%20say%20they%20would%20choose%20NOTA%20as%20%26quot%3Bthey%20did%20not%20like%20what%20BJP%20did%26quot%3B%2C%20Ms%20Mahajan%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20explained%20to%20them%20that%20BJP%20has%20done%20nothing%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20that%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20party%20is%20sticking%20to%20its%20core%20ideology%20and%20our%20candidate%20(Mr%20Lalwani)%20is%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20so%20they%20should%20vote%20for%20BJP%20instead%20of%20NOTA.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715431140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-01%2Fnota_650x400_71515408891.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbetrayed-by-indore-pick-congress-bats-for-nota-to-teach-bjp-a-lesson-5640555%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jolted%20by%20its%20Indore%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20withdrawing%20its%20nomination%20and%20then%20rubbing%20salt%20in%20its%20wounds%20by%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20now%20banking%20on%20the%20NOTA%20-%20none%20of%20the%20above%20-%20option%20to%20%26quot%3Bteach%20a%20lesson%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbetrayed-by-indore-pick-congress-bats-for-nota-to-teach-bjp-a-lesson-5640555%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbetrayed-by-indore-pick-congress-bats-for-nota-to-teach-bjp-a-lesson-5640555%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbetrayed-by-indore-pick-congress-bats-for-nota-to-teach-bjp-a-lesson-5640555%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20will%20fight%20with%20its%20%E2%80%98fingernails%E2%80%99%3A%20Netanyahu%20defies%20Biden%20ultimatum%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715431111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110037264%2Cimgsize-1316785.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-will-fight-with-its-fingernails-netanyahu-defies-biden-ultimatum%2Farticleshow%2F110037169.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20a