3B%3Cem%3EAur%20jab%20itna%20jyada%20dete%20hi%20the%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20ji%20ko%2C%20lekin%20aap%20inko%20dijiye%20abhi%20toh%20naujawan%20hain%2C%20ye%20aage%20badhega%20aur%20khoob%20kaam%20karega%3C%2Fem%3E%20(You%20used%20to%20vote%20overwhelmingly%20for%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20ji%2C%20now%20vote%20for%20Chirag%20Paswan.%20He%20is%20young%20and%20will%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20work)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20amid%20loud%20cheers%20and%20a%20round%20of%20applause.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20acrimony%20between%20Mr%20Kumar%20and%20Junior%20Paswan%2C%20both%20back%20in%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%2C%20appeared%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan%2C%2041%2C%20has%20pledged%20eternal%20loyalty%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20In%20a%20dramatic%20Hanuman%20metaphor%2C%20he%20has%20said%20that%20the%20image%20of%20PM%20Modi%20is%20seared%20in%20his%20heart%20and%20will%20be%20visible%20to%20anyone%20if%2C%20like%20Lord%20Hanuman%2C%20he%20slashes%20open%20his%20chest.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20terribly%20missing%20my%20father.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20when%20I%20will%20have%20to%20file%20nomination%20papers%20with%20him%20not%20around.%20He%20was%20there%20to%20bless%20me%20both%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Paswan%2C%20who%20calls%20himself%20a%20%26quot%3BYuva%20Bihari%26quot%3B%2C%20told%20reporters%20after%20filing%20his%20nomination%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20has%20got%20five%20seats%20in%20Bihar%20as%20per%20the%20seat-sharing%20formula%20decided%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20national%20president%20of%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%2C%20founded%20by%20late%20Paswan%2C%20until%20it%20was%20split%20in%202021%20by%20the%20latter's%20younger%20brother%20Pashupati%20Kumar%20Paras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPashupati%20Paras%20currently%20holds%20the%20Hajipur%20seat%2C%20which%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20fifth%20phase%20on%20May%2020%20in%20the%20ongoing%20marathon%20six%20week%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040%20seats%20in%20Bihar%20are%20undergoing%20polls%20in%20all%20seven%20phases.%20In%202019%2C%20BJP-led%20NDA%20swept%20the%20state%20by%20winning%2039%20out%20of%2040%20seats%2C%20while%20Congress%20won%20just%20one%20seat.%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20RJD%2C%20a%20formidable%20force%20in%20the%20state%2C%20failed%20to%20open%20its%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahagathbandhan%20(Grand%20Alliance)%2C%20the%20opposition%20coalition%20in%20Bihar%2C%20including%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20Left%20parties%2C%20have%20announced%20that%20the%20RJD%2C%20its%20largest%20constituent%2C%20will%20contest%2026%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20BJP%20and%20JD(U)%20will%20contest%20on%2017%20and%2016%20seats%2C%20respectively.%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi's%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(HAM)%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Morcha%20will%20contest%20one%20seat%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715427660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Foo7nui58_nitish-chirag-1200_625x300_11_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumars-vote-for-ram-vilas-paswan-appeal-then-a-correction-5639981%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20today%20appeared%20to%20be%20asking%20for%20votes%20for%20late%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20the%20veteran%20leader%20from%20Bihar%20who%20died%20in%202020.%20However%2C%20the%2073-year-old%20Chief%20Minister%20quickly%20course%20corrected%20and%20pitched%20for%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20the%20late%20leader's%20son.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumars-vote-for-ram-vilas-p